{
  "text": "We propose that ANG II inhibits H \u03e9 -ATPase-mediated proton export in parallel with activation of Na \u03e9 /H \u03e9 exchange. It was demonstrated earlier that when H \u03e9 -ATPase is inhibited by bafilomycin A 1 , activation of Na \u03e9 /H \u03e9 exchange occurs and pH i remains stable [CITATION_1] . Currently, we do not have sufficient information to determine whether a specific mechanism may exist to activate Na \u03e9 /H \u03e9 exchange when H \u03e9 -ATPase-mediated proton export is inhibited.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "1224060"
